wiki.content: "So What" was the lead single from P!nk's most recent album, Funhouse, which was released on October 27, 2008. P!nk performed the song at the MTV Video Music Awards on September 7, 2008. The single is P!nk's first #1 solo hit in the U.S., reaching the top spot in its fourth week on the Hot 100. "So What" was also performed at the Australian Music Awards in November 2008 in Sydney.
